    <div class="contentDiv bg-dark " id="homePage">
        <strong id="instructions" class="text-white">
            {{!-- <img class="icon" id="homeIcon" src='film-icon.png' /> --}}

            Use the navigation bar on the top to go through our website's features:<br>


            Home - Return to this page<br>
            Search - Search for movies from TheMovieDB based on key words, actors and directors<br>
            Favorites - Save your favorite movies to a list from the search<br>
            Recommendations - Generate recommendations for movies based on your favorites<br>
            Settings - Change your username or password<br>
            Logout - End your session<br>
        </strong>
        
    </div>
